<title>TURKEY: Turkish markets to shut for holiday April 17-24.</title>
<headline>Turkish markets to shut for holiday April 17-24.</headline>
<dateline>ISTANBUL 1997-04-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>All Turkish markets will close for the 6-1/2 day Islamic holiday of Eid al-Adha and the Children's Day national holiday from mid-Thursday, April 17, market officials said.</p>
<p>They will reopen on April 24.</p>
